        "TileImage": "$($repository 0dfaea51-3c36-4722-9eff-f1e7ef139878).Image",
        "Description": "47, NO TIME TO EXPLAIN! Caruso and De Santis have linked the virus to a biometric trigger. If their heart rates spike from seeing you or hearing an alarm, the virus is unleashed. To stop it, you must ensure their hearts never beat again.\r\rYou have 1:52 before the failsafe triggers automatically. No recordings. No suspicions. No disguises. You must use the mansion car to escape.\r\rSTAY OUT OF SIGHT AND KILL THEM NOW! GO!",
